        <!-- Product Description -->
        <div id="description" class="tab-panel">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Product Description</h2>
          <p>The RMC-2000i is an industrial-grade, cellular-based monitoring and control system engineered for precise, real-time data tracking and remote equipment control. Ideal for monitoring pump status/run times, high-level alarms, and 4–20mA sensor inputs such as pressure, flow, current, and more, the RMC-2000i also offers pump control capabilities for complete site automation.

</p>Designed with large terminal blocks for simplified wiring and built-in 4–20mA signal isolators for enhanced reliability, the RMC-2000i is a rugged upgrade from traditional SCADA and autodialer systems. It shares the same core specifications as the RMC-2000 but is optimized for easier installation and dependable sensor performance.

</p>Whether you're managing lift stations, industrial wellheads, or mechanical systems like boilers and chillers, the RMC-2000i delivers cost-effective, cloud-connected control.

</p>Have questions? Call us at 866-310-1055 – we're happy to help.</p>
        </div>
